        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/0e095fc2124344e1e14228ff20039ac1_5029933772297738972.png",
                "id": "talent52553",
                "key": "Khanda Barrier-Buster ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Khanda Barrier-Buster "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>. This character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vijnana Suffusion</span>.<br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\"><br>Vijnana Suffusion</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached uses a Charged Attack: </span>Their<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> Physical DMG </span>dealt will be converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span> and after the Skill DMG is finalized, summon 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Clusterbloom Arrow</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/f516d2b769cb6a5d5a1cb65ee009c970_8214898441424799541.png",
                "id": "talent22748",
                "key": "Vijnana-Phala Mine ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Vijnana-Phala Mine "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 4 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/09/35428890/28bd8ee6fb2d010cf70cf78e4d3a2fd6_2741975943608586043.png",
                "id": "talent6420",
                "key": "Fashioner's Tanglevine Shaft ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Fashioner's Tanglevine Shaft "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span> (Can stack. Max 2 Stacks.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_873359235918325617.png",
                "id": "talent95294",
                "key": "Clusterbloom Arrow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/35428890/610be0cd5a38653316e32f23c8abf0e8_7223927240321678896.png",
                "title": "Clusterbloom Arrow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_2533132220365968813.png",
                "id": "talent6254",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Before your Action Phase, should the total number of your Elemental Dice be even, your Normal Attack will be considered a Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Piercing DMG</span></strong></p><p>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bounses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_6854294694600111449.png",
                "id": "talent91828",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
